ok theory time!
So a dove is shown having been shot by an arrow in the beginning, in the middle of a battlefield. And a white dove reprecents: god, hope, peace and messengers. And birds in general are reprisentetive of freedom. An Arrow to the chest reprecents both love and war. So this could be hinting at the bird as a messenger for peace, hope, freedom and even god being shot down by war and hatred, making people lose hope for peace and freedom, and stopping god from reaching us. Then jin with love then takes care of the dove so it could fly again, this states that what we need is to spread love and to care for others in order to stop pain and suffering and to gain happines etc.
